Racing on Rails is a bike racing association schedule, results, competitions, and membership database and website.

Open source (MIT license)
Ruby on Rails
http://rubyonrails.org/

Documentation, quick start, and issue tracker
http://trac.butlerpress.com/racing_on_rails

Google Group
http://groups.google.com/group/racing-on-rails

Source Code
http://github.com/scottwillson/racing_on_rails/tree/master
